@page "/info/faq"

<div class="faq-main__container">
    <div class="faq_content__container">
        <div class="faq-title__container">
            <h3>FAQ</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>What payment methods do you accept?</h4>
            <p>
                We accept major credit cards, debit cards, and other secure payment methods.
                You can find the complete list during the checkout process.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>How can I track my order?</h4>
            <p>
                Once your order is shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number.
                Use this number to track your order on our website or the courier's site.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>What is your return policy?</h4>
            <p>
                Our return policy allows for returns within 30 days of receiving your order.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>Do you ship internationally?</h4>
            <p>
                Yes, we offer international shipping. Shipping costs and delivery times may vary.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>Are the product colors accurate in photos?</h4>
            <p>
                We strive to display accurate product colors, but variations may occur due to monitor settings.
                Refer to our product descriptions for additional details.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>How can I contact customer support?</h4>
            <p>
                You can reach our customer support team by email or through our <a class="faq-container__link" href="/info/contactus">Contact Us</a> page. We aim to respond within [X] hours.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>Can I modify or cancel my order?</h4>
            <p>
                Once an order is placed, modifications or cancellations may not be possible.
                Please review your order carefully before confirming.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <h4>Are my personal details secure?</h4>
            <p>
                Yes, we prioritize the security of your personal information. Refer to our <a class="faq-container__link" href="/info/privacypolicy">Privacy Policy</a> for details on
                how we handle and protect your data.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>